OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G21/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FFour objectives are set out: audience
OL,7,Fprotection, accessibility,
OL,8,Fproportionality, and future-proofing
OL,9,FOfcom's powers.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
