OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,GKEEPING PUBLIC SERVICE CONTENT VISIBLE
OL,8,FChapter four turns to making PSM
OL,9,Fcontent discoverable on the platforms
OL,10,Faudiences now use.
OL,12,FThe government's strong preference is
OL,13,Ffor voluntary, industry-led deals, and
OL,14,Fit points to the BBC's January 2026
OL,15,Fagreement with YouTube (which debuted
OL,16,Fwith Winter Olympics coverage in
OL,17,FFebruary) and ITV's use of YouTube for
OL,18,Fthe Brit Awards.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14923
SC,0023
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G23/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt welcomes ongoing dialogue between
OL,7,FYouTube and PSM providers and urges it
OL,8,Fto accelerate, while making clear it is
OL,9,Fnot deciding on legislation yet and
OL,10,Fwants more evidence and time for
OL,11,Fvoluntary progress.
OL,13,FIt is consulting on whether all PSM
OL,14,Fcontent, or priority genres such as
OL,15,Fnews and children's programming, should
OL,16,Fbe covered, and across which devices.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
