OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G24/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn a move likely to please sports
OL,7,Faudiences, the government confirms it
OL,8,Fintends to legislate, when
OL,9,Fparliamentary time allows, to extend
OL,10,Fthe Listed Events regime ` which keeps
OL,11,F"crown jewels" such as Wimbledon and
OL,12,Fthe FA Cup Final free-to-air ` to cover
OL,13,Fon-demand rights as well as live
OL,14,Fcoverage, reflecting how audiences
OL,15,Fincreasingly watch sport after the
OL,16,Fevent.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
