OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G25/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,GA NEW SHAPE FOR PUBLIC SERVICE
OL,7,GBROADCASTING
OL,9,FThe paper makes plain the financial
OL,10,Fstrain on the six PSM providers ` the
OL,11,FBBC, ITV, STV, Channel 4, Channel 5 and
OL,12,FS4C.
OL,14,FThe BBC's licence fee income has fallen
OL,15,Fby more than 30 per cent in real terms
OL,16,Fover a decade, the commercial
OL,17,Fproviders' combined advertising revenue
OL,18,Fof around #1.7 billion in 2024 was more
OL,19,Fthan #700 million lower in real terms
OL,20,Fthan in 2018, and PSM content output
OL,21,Fhas declined year on year since 2022.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14926
SC,0026
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G26/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn response, the government will
OL,7,Fexplore moving away from regulating PSM
OL,8,Fproviders through broadcast licences
OL,9,Faltogether, which would allow greater
OL,10,Fflexibility over who qualifies and what
OL,11,Fobligations and benefits apply.
OL,13,FIt presents three illustrative models:
OL,15,F- one centred on designated PSM
OL,16,Finstitutions (closest to today's
OL,17,Fsystem, potentially with a two-tier
OL,18,Fstructure admitting some new
OL,19,Fproviders);
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14927
SC,0027
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G27/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,F- one centred on individual PSM
OL,7,Fservices, which could include a
OL,8,Fdocumentary or history channel on
OL,9,FYouTube gaining designation;
OL,11,F- and a content-centric approach, in
OL,12,Fwhich any output meeting an evolving
OL,13,Fdefinition of public service content
OL,14,Fwould qualify for benefits such as
OL,15,Ffunding or prominence.
OL,17,FEach retains the BBC as the largest
OL,18,Fprovider.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14928
SC,0028
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G28/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FFour guiding principles are proposed:
OL,7,Funiversality, a wide range of
OL,8,Fhigh-quality public service content,
OL,9,Fsystemic sustainability through a more
OL,10,Fresilient mix of providers, and a
OL,11,Frebalanced compact in which benefits
OL,12,Fremain proportionate to obligations.
OL,14,FThe stated ambition is to reverse the
OL,15,Frecent decline in output and open the
OL,16,Fsystem to new entrants, while
OL,17,Fprotecting the independent production
OL,18,Fsector and the nations and regions.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
