OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,GTHE WIDER PICTURE AND NEXT STEPS
OL,8,FThroughout, the paper sets its
OL,9,Fproposals against the market context:
OL,10,Fvideo-sharing platforms and streaming
OL,11,Fnow account for 74 per cent of video
OL,12,Ftime among 16 to 24 year-olds, YouTube
OL,13,Fis the most-watched service for
OL,14,Fchildren aged four to 15, and the UK
OL,15,Fdrew #4.8 billion of inward film and TV
OL,16,Finvestment in 2024.
OL,18,FIt builds on the Media Act 2024 and the
OL,19,FCreative Industries Sector Plan,
OL,20,Fincluding a #75 million Screen Growth
OL,21,FPackage launched in April 2026.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14930
SC,0030
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G30/30
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWS+CGovernment green paper outlines
OL,4,CFreeview switch-off options
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe consultation ` which runs until
OL,7,F31st August ` poses 30 questions
OL,8,Fspanning market context, news and PSM
OL,9,Fprominence, the future of TV
OL,10,Fdistribution and regulation, media
OL,11,Fliteracy, a new PSM system, and
OL,12,Fequalities impacts.
OL,14,FFinal decisions will be set out in a
OL,15,Fforthcoming white paper, with the
OL,16,Fgovernment's verdict on the future of
OL,17,FTV distribution expected later this
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,23,EPub: 23-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
